#Install
安装软件请按如下步骤

## install xampp
[中文参考网址](https://www.apachefriends.org/zh_cn/index.html)

1. 直接下载安装至 C:\tool\common\xampp
2. 启动
### confict:  port 443 is used by vm
config vm's share port to 4443(just is not 443)

## install composer
[中文参考网址](http://docs.phpcomposer.com/)
[英文参考网站](https://getcomposer.org/)
```cmd
cd C:\tool\common\xampp\php
php -r "readfile('https://getcomposer.org/installer');" | php
echo @php "%~dp0composer.phar" %*>composer.bat
```
[see](http://docs.phpcomposer.com/00-intro.html)


## install